{"tid":2128010,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"藍田門診深喉唾液樣本瓶條碼　部分與樣本包條碼不符","createTime":"2020-07-27T15:56:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T16:30:01.000Z","uid":39464,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4c76611d104fb54a392280cf5027895ee64d5125","tid":2128010,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T15:56:56.000Z","msg":"醫院管理局（醫管局）今日（27日）表示，今日起協助衛生防護中心在22間普通科門診診所試行派發深喉唾液樣本包，檢視運作流程時發現，藍田普通科門診診所派發的樣本包，部分貼於樣本瓶的條碼，有可能與樣本包內個人資料表格的條碼不相同。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局已要求普通科門診診所職員在收集樣本瓶時特別提醒市民，再一次小心核對條碼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200727/s00001/1595863394605/%e6%96%b0%e5%86%a0%e8%82%ba%e7%82%8e-%e8%97%8d%e7%94%b0%e9%96%80%e8%a8%ba%e6%b7%b1%e5%96%89%e5%94%be%e6%b6%b2%e6%a8%a3%e6%9c%ac%e7%93%b6%e6%a2%9d%e7%a2%bc-%e9%83%a8%e5%88%86%e8%88%87%e6%a8%a3%e6%9c%ac%e5%8c%85%e6%a2%9d%e7%a2%bc%e4%b8%8d%e7%ac%a6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200727%2Fs00001%2F1595863394605%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e-%25e8%2597%258d%25e7%2594%25b0%25e9%2596%2580%25e8%25a8%25ba%25e6%25b7%25b1%25e5%2596%2589%25e5%2594%25be%25e6%25b6%25b2%25e6%25a8%25a3%25e6%259c%25ac%25e7%2593%25b6%25e6%25a2%259d%25e7%25a2%25bc-%25e9%2583%25a8%25e5%2588%2586%25e8%2588%2587%25e6%25a8%25a3%25e6%259c%25ac%25e5%258c%2585%25e6%25a2%259d%25e7%25a2%25bc%25e4%25b8%258d%25e7%25ac%25a6&d=oFI5KSBgBGvHra6dYUznBnpsBjqOi2zFRj9KJcX5ApM%3D&h=f29eb5e4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200727%2Fs00001%2F1595863394605%2F%25e6%2596%25b0%25e5%2586%25a0%25e8%2582%25ba%25e7%2582%258e-%25e8%2597%258d%25e7%2594%25b0%25e9%2596%2580%25e8%25a8%25ba%25e6%25b7%25b1%25e5%2596%2589%25e5%2594%25be%25e6%25b6%25b2%25e6%25a8%25a3%25e6%259c%25ac%25e7%2593%25b6%25e6%25a2%259d%25e7%25a2%25bc-%25e9%2583%25a8%25e5%2588%2586%25e8%2588%2587%25e